Package: pgxR
Title: Pharmacogenomics Dose-Response Analysis with Population Context
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Qualia", "Hooker", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "lia.hooker@vai.edu")
Description: A toolkit for fitting, visualizing, and comparing
    dose-response curves across cancer cell lines. Provides functions for
    IC50/AUC extraction, population-stratified visualization by ancestry
    and genomic feature status as well as downstream correlation with
    omics data.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    drc,
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    purrr,
    ggplot2,
    ggrepel,
    stats,
    utils
